@node Quoting of newline
@section Quoting of newline

Because of the way newline is quoted this will not work:

@verbatim
  echo 1,2,3 | parallel -vkd, "echo 'a{}b'"
@end verbatim

However, these will all work:

@verbatim
  echo 1,2,3 | parallel -vkd, echo a{}b
  echo 1,2,3 | parallel -vkd, "echo 'a'{}'b'"
  echo 1,2,3 | parallel -vkd, "echo 'a'"{}"'b'"
@end verbatim

@node Speed
@section Speed

